long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Extension designed to help users shop on chinese platforms like taobao, weidian, 1688 etc. with shipping agents.
 Current features:
- Automatic conversion for every detected agent/marketplace link
- Automatic Finds.ly QC link generation on supported websites.
- Manual link conversion
- To get your code, go to our discord (discord.gg/keith), and type /ext on any channel. (to be able to do that, you need to solve captcha on verification channel)
